des:
Have you ever wanted the perfect way to end a conversation, or dismiss an unwelcome visitor? Well now you can. Don't take our word for it just see what the critics said.

★☆☆☆☆ "Why would I need this. Get off my property at once. Smithers Release the hounds." C.M. Burns, Springfield.

★☆☆☆☆ "Meow?" Scooter.

★☆☆☆☆ "Just how clean are your work surfaces." D.E. Trotter, Nelson Mandela House Peckham London.
